<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8277019">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8277019/" class="title-link">序言节选</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8277019"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/127918519/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u127918519-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/127918519/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">新思文化</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-06"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-06 14:10:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8277019_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本卷的一个主题是，近代政治制度的基本要素以及人们对于它们的态度是逐渐形成的，而且过程时断时续。一般来说，要到它们形成后，人们才开始对它们产生理解，过程也是同样的缓慢而断续，但并非总是如此。黑格尔说，哲学本质上是回溯性的，但我们不可能不注意到，有的思想似乎是...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8277019_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8277019_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










